### Low-Code / No-Code Security Automation Project

The **CoLab-AI-App** is an email filtering and classification system built entirely using **no-code and low-code tools** including **AppSheet**, **Google Sheets**, **Make (Integromat)**, and **Gmail**.  

This project demonstrates modern security automation techniques without writing heavy codeâ€”perfect for rapid prototyping, SOC workflows, and real-world email triage use cases.

---

## ðŸš€ Project Overview

The purpose of this application is to **automate the filtering, categorization, and routing of incoming emails**, especially those that may be:

- Suspicious  
- Potentially malicious  
- High priority  
- Related to business operations  

The workflow uses automation tools to gather email metadata, classify messages, and present them in an AppSheet dashboard for easy action and review.

---

## ðŸ›  Tools Used

| Tool | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| **AppSheet** | Front-end UI for email review, tagging, and filtering |
| **Google Sheets** | Backend database storing email metadata |
| **Make (Integromat)** | Workflow automation to fetch emails and update data |
| **Gmail** | Email source, filtering conditions, and triggers |

